The paper deals with information security, cryptography, and steganography, which are all related to the field of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed method is specifically designed for true colour images, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also involves image processing techniques such as image transposition and gray-level modification, which are relevant to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multiple encryption algorithms and stego key-based encryption suggests that the paper may also belong to the information theory (cs.IT) category. Finally, the paper emphasizes the importance of security in the proposed scheme, which could also be relevant to the cybernetics (cs.CY) category.
